From: Mystery SD <105407900+SilentDemonSD@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Fri, 12 Jun 2026 12:11:49 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add Mega upload/clone support, Drive Categories, and
 infrastructure improvements

- Add Mega folder upload support /m -i no -m f_name -up mega
- Add Mega clone support (file-only) via /clone
- Introduce DRIVE_CATEGORY_MODE, categories.txt, and enhanced GDrive Categories (-gc) /ctsel
- Add HELPER_STRINGS and IMG_SOURCES support (2 more)
- Improve Web UI, SABnzbd, qBittorrent, NZB, proxy endpoints, and Cloudflare tunnel integration (Proper Working)
- Add exception handling, logging, and database synchronization fixes !!
- Improve thread safety, connection handling, proxy headers, and Docker deployment
- General bug fixes, cleanup, testing, and debugging across modules

~ MysterySD
