+   The bot runs behind a Cloudflare quick tunnel by default. Check the tunnel URL:
+
+   ```bash
+   docker compose logs tunnel
+   ```
+
+   You'll see a `https://*.trycloudflare.com` URL — that's your bot's web UI.
+
+   To stop:
+
+   ```bash
